<div class="thumbinner" style="width:302px;"><a href="/wiki/File:John_Ralston_Saul.jpg" class="image" title="John Ralston Saul delivers a lecture at the University of Alberta on November 17, 2006."><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a2/John_Ralston_Saul.jpg/300px-John_Ralston_Saul.jpg" width="300" height="448" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
